                    <p>At TKIL Industries Pvt. Ltd., we have two manufacturing units in the industrially developed areas of Pune and Hyderabad. These units have 'state of the Art', machine shop and excellent fabrication facilities aided by testing equipment of international standards catering to a wide range of equipment for core industries such as mining, cement, power generation, and sugar. Both units follow highest standards of safety, productivity and quality.</p>

